    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-10-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-10-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="159"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d159">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Conger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-10-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 10, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Yours of 9th received. <hi rend="italic">Boston</hi> and <hi rend="italic"
                        >Petrel</hi> with marine guards left Manila for Taku October 4. Should
                    arrive October 14. Order guards to Peking only in case of necessity.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hay.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
